@scottyaustin34 Hi Scott,
How can we assist you?
Kind regards, Daphne

@yamanouchi Hello,
please send your request to specialcases@austrian.com
Best regards, Alessandra

@homeroomtravel Hi Francesca, I'm sorry to hear your luggage wasn't duly delivered. In order to file a claim for any compensation, please proceed to our webpage by using the following link.
https://t.co/1jYyfcuAde
Best regards, Shawn

@NadiehClarkson Hello,
yes we still recommend 2 or 3 hours before departure time.
 Best regards, Alessandra

@PriftiJorgo (1/2) Dear Martin,
I am sorry that you had to wait so long. We currently have a lot of calls again. At the moment, our passengers also need more time for their concerns. Of course, we also want to take the time that each passenger needs. 
I can assure you

@Dmi3Rob Dear Dmitry,
we try our best to avoid flight irregularities, delays and cancellations. Please be assured that we never delay a flight without good reason. I hope that your future travels will be according to plan again.
 Best regards, Alessandra

@SpevakRobert Hello Robert,
we are sorry that you were affected by a flight irregularity. We of course do try to operate our flights according to schedule, however it is sometimes unavoidable to delay or cancel flights on short notice.
Best regards, Alessandra

@arnon86 Dear Arnon,
our Baggage team will do all they can to reunite you with it as soon as possible. If you've still not received an update after 72 hours, please let us know. 
Best regards, Alessandra
